#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "xz / lzma"
msgstr "xz / lzma इति"

#. Tag: author
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "<firstname>Per Øyvind</firstname><surname> Karlsen</surname>"
msgstr "<firstname>प्रति Øyvind</firstname><surname> कार्लसेन्</surname>"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "ROLES_OF_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "अनुवादकानां_भूमिका"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "Xz is a compression program"
msgstr "Xz एकः संपीडनकार्यक्रमः अस्ति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The xz KIO worker is not directly usable, and is intended for use as a "
"filter. For example, the tar KIO worker can filter a file through the xz KIO "
"worker, in order to display the contents of a <literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar.lzma</literal> or <literal role=\"extension\">tar.xz</literal> file "
"directly in a &konqueror; window."
msgstr ""
"xz KIO कार्यकर्ता प्रत्यक्षतया उपयोगयोग्यः नास्ति, तथा च फ़िल्टररूपेण उपयोगाय अभिप्रेतः । "
"यथा, tar KIO कार्यकर्ता xz KIO कार्यकर्तुः माध्यमेन सञ्चिकां छानयितुं शक्नोति, यत् "
"<literal role=\"extension\">tar.lzma</literal> अथवा <literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar इत्यस्य सामग्रीं प्रदर्शयितुं शक्नोति .xz</literal> सञ्चिकायां प्रत्यक्षतया "
"&konqueror; कोष्ठ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on a file compressed with a <literal role=\"extension\">.lzma</"
"literal> or <literal role=\"extension\">tar.xz</literal> in &konqueror;, "
"this KIO worker is used to uncompress it and display it as a normal "
"(uncompressed) file."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् &konqueror;मध्ये <literal role=\"extension\">.lzma</literal> अथवा "
"<literal role=\"extension\">tar.xz</literal> इत्यनेन संकुचितसञ्चिकायां क्लिक् करोति "
"तर्हि अयं KIO कार्यकर्ता असंपीडयितुं उपयुज्यते it तथा सामान्य (असंपीडित) सञ्चिकारूपेण "
"प्रदर्शयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are a developer, and would like to use the xz filter, you can find "
"documentation on using KIO workers at <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org"
"\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् विकासकः अस्ति, तथा च xz फ़िल्टरस्य उपयोगं कर्तुम् इच्छति, तर्हि भवान् <ulink "
"url=\"http://techbase.kde.org\">http://techbase.kde.org< इत्यत्र KIO कार्यकर्तृणां "
"उपयोगस्य दस्तावेजीकरणं प्राप्तुं शक्नोति /उलिंक्>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the manual: <ulink url=\"man:/xz\">xz</ulink>."
msgstr "पुस्तिकाम् पश्यन्तु: <ulink url=\"man:/xz\">xz</ulink> ।"
